Dialogue: 12,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Tới kịp rồi…
Dialogue: 12,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Phải khâu lại thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Này.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:14.61,0:18:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Sao lại thế này?
Dialogue: 12,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhâm Thị đại nhân.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Nô tì có thể xin ngưu hoàng được không?
Dialogue: 12,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Giờ đâu phải lúc nói chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Mặt ngươi…
Dialogue: 12,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,sao lại thành ra thế này?
